  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink27-kilavi"> talaimakaḷ maṉaikkaṇ varuṅkālattu vārātu tāḻttuḻi ‘puṟattoḻukkam
          uḷatāyiṟṟu’ eṉak karuti varuntum talaimakaṭkut tōḻi colliyatu. </p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="Aink27">
          <l> cennelañ ceṟuviṟ katirkoṇṭu kaḷvaṉ</l>
          <l> ṟaṇṇaka maṇṇaḷaic cellu mūraṟ</l>
          <l> kelvaḷai nekiḻac cāa</l>
          <l> yalla luḻappa tevaṉko laṉṉāy.</l>

        </lg>
        <lg xml:lang="en">
          <l> The fact that [we] bear unhappiness,</l>
          <l> being so exhausted that [our] bright bangles become loose </l>
            <l>because of the man from the village</l>
          <l rend="indent2"> where the crab, having taken ears from the red paddy field, </l>
          <l rend="indent2"> goes into [its] cool interior earth hole:</l>
          <l> What [of it], mother?</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
  </text>
